{"tid":1420861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每一次完咗我哋都好需要一個反思會","createTime":"2019-08-06T06:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T06:18:05.000Z","uid":71377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9c14b8e949ed10d966a5a22c1341ee5c505afff1","tid":1420861,"uid":71377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:02:40.000Z","msg":"6月9號到而家 每一次我哋都吸收咗經驗值 之後又唔同嘅進化方向<br />\n有啲變咗狂戰士 有啲變咗法師 有啲變咗裝甲兵<br />\n就算係和理非有好多都已經開始有催淚彈經驗，但係我哋吸收咗咁多經驗之後始終都冇一個平台畀我哋檢討，而唔同嘅進化方向又好可能有好多磨擦出嚟<br />\n所以我好希望喺呢度舉行第一個反思會 等大家可以集合經驗減低摩擦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90cc5e54fe32dcbb06a3ac507a791ec06ba41e3c","tid":1420861,"uid":71377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:04:29.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"6b4bcd3160ad6ce504d224c6e71badc829d08048","tid":1420861,"uid":71377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:04:39.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"e6d48d402b2f08f6dc08fa407d53cc8833ceccc1","tid":1420861,"uid":71377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:04:50.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"213fe7292996538efaacb1e9b8905aeb07d68aaa","tid":1420861,"uid":71377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:05:00.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"13e2a3c0c9d1729224aa6ea55731cf82b9c2b044","tid":1420861,"uid":71377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:05:10.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"45a79cdb334f2e9c788a48bedb28ae9049a9616e","tid":1420861,"uid":71377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:05:20.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"79f48b2696370d81b06cedc3890376cced1711f7","tid":1420861,"uid":71377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:05:30.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"36f072ea680cebe9d659090a38bf2d07467278d3","tid":1420861,"uid":71377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:05:40.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"a714ec0cf1e0397